# Project Structure Guide

This project is a Next.js application with the following key files and directories:

- [src/](mdc:src): Main application source code.
  - [app/](mdc:src/app): Routing, pages, and layouts.
    - (auth): Authentication flows (login, signup, reset-password) and their components.
    - admin, marketing, organization, products: Feature-specific sections.
    - api/: API route handlers (e.g., auth).
    - globals.css, layout.tsx, favicon.ico: Global styles and layout.
  - [components/](mdc:src/components): Shared React components.
    - ui/: Reusable UI elements (button, input, label, tabs).
  - [lib/](mdc:src/lib): Utility functions and authentication logic.
  - [middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts): Next.js middleware for request handling.
  - [env.ts](mdc:src/env.ts): Environment variable management.
  - [server/](mdc:src/server): Server-side logic (e.g., auth).

- [prisma/](mdc:prisma): Prisma ORM database schema and SQLite file.
  - schema.prisma, db.sqlite

- [public/](mdc:public): Static assets (SVGs, images).

- [specs/](mdc:specs): (Purpose not detailed; likely for tests or specifications.)
- [ai_docs/](mdc:ai_docs): (Purpose not detailed; likely for AI-related documentation.)

- [CLAUDE.md](mdc:CLAUDE.md): Rule file for Claude Code (don't use in Cursor).
- [components.json](mdc:components.json): Component registry or configuration.
- [oxlint.json](mdc:oxlint.json): Linting configuration.
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts): Next.js configuration.
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts.
- [pnpm-lock.yaml](mdc:pnpm-lock.yaml): Dependency lockfile for pnpm.
- [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs): PostCSS configuration.
- [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project documentation and setup instructions.
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript configuration.

